<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <link rel="icon" href="public/images/logo.svg" type="image/x-icon">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/ac1e998d8e.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <title>Snapsec - Your Security, Centralized</title>
</head>

<body style="background: #f0f9ff; margin: 20px; padding: 0; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #334155;">
    <table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 100%; max-width: 619px; border-radius: 10px; border: 2px solid #e0f2fe; background-color: #ffffff; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1); color: #334155; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px 30px;">
        <tr>
            <td align="center" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
                <img src="https://snapsec.co/logos/blue-medium.png" alt="Snapsec Logo" style="width: 60px;">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <h3 style="text-align: center; margin: 10px; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 500; color: #1e293b;">Verification Code</h3>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <table align="center" style="margin: 0 auto;">
                    <tr style="line-height:normal;">
                        <td style="padding-right:8px;">
                            <img width="20" height="20" src="https://robohash.org/{{email}}" alt="" style="border-radius: 50%;">
                        </td>
                        <td>
                            <a href="mailto:{{email}}" style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; color: #1e293b; text-decoration: none;">
                                {{email}}
                            </a>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <hr style="border: 1px solid #bae6fd; background: #bae6fd; margin: 30px auto; width: 100%;">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; text-align: center; word-spacing: 2px; font-weight: 500; color: #1e293b; margin-top: 30px;">
                    Use the following verification code to complete your authentication:
                </p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td align="center" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                <div style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9 0%, #0284c7 100%); padding: 20px 40px; border-radius: 10px; border: 2px solid #0ea5e9; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.3);">
                    <span style="font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: 8px; font-family: 'Inter', monospace;">
                        {{otp}}
                    </span>
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; text-align: center; color: #64748b; margin-top: 25px;">
                    This code will expire in <strong style="color: #1e293b;">{{expiryMinutes}} minutes</strong>.
                </p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <p style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; text-align: center; color: #64748b; margin-top: 20px;">
                    If you didn't request this verification code, please ignore this email or contact support if you have concerns.
                </p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td align="center" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px;">
                <a href="https://{{base_url}}/auth/login" style="line-height: 16px; color: #ffffff; font-weight: 500; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9 0%, #0284c7 100%); border-radius: 6px; min-width: 90px; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.3); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">Go to Snapsec Suite</a>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="font-size: 13px; text-align: center; margin-top: 40px;">
                <p style="font-size: 13px; text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; color: #64748b;">You can also manage your account at</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td align="center" style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 16.94px; color: #1e293b; text-align: center;">
                <a href="https://{{base_url}}/account/security" style="color:#0ea5e9;font-size: 10px; text-decoration: none;">https://{{base_url}}/account/security</a>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <p style="font-size: 12px; text-align: center; margin: 20px auto; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #64748b;">
        You received this email as part of the two-factor authentication process for your Suite Account.
    </p>
</body>

</html>
